Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:03.15,Left,,0,0,0,,Preklad a časovanie:\NTsukki
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:06.15,Left,,0,0,0,,Korekcia:\NYouko Akira
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:10.15,Left,,0,0,0,,Titulky od GAW-Subs\Nwww.gawsubs.com\N2016
